          "title": "[WIP] [wallet] Couple minimum change with minimum relay fee",
          "body": "Coupling `MIN_CHANGE` with  the minimum relay fee (and thus dust) turns out to fix #6522.\n\nAssuming that a user should be able to send a small amount even though their wallet consists of mostly small/dust inputs, I get\n\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/math/5/e/a/5eaa9803b32f3f69f5489eae256545cb.png\">\n\nâ‡’ `MIN_CHANGE = ((DEFAULT_MIN_RELAY_TX_FEE/1000.) * MAX_STANDARD_TX_SIZE / COIN) = 0.001`\n",
